{
  "texts": [
    "This leads us to the following conclusion: if the result does not truly fascinate the writer or he/she is not ready to interact with a chatbot for a long time, it can be an obstacle for the creative writing process using an AI agent.",
    "However, a detailed study of chatbot capabilities, as well as a conscious approach to using AI in creative writing and not relying solely on its results, will help improve the novel, find new ways to make the story more fascinating and develop an interesting plot and characters.",
    "Generation of dialogues.",
    "The chatbot generates human-like dialogues based on the previous information about the novel.",
    "The ability of ChatGPT to generate high-quality dialogues varies from time to time; sometimes, answer regenerating or prompt clarifying may help."
  ]
}